roup structure of the finite groups of\nexceptional Lie type. For instance, we show that for $n \\ge 10$, $\\text{Alt}_n$\nand $\\text{Sym}_n$, as well as numerous other almost simple groups, cannot\noccur as a maximal subgroup of an almost simple group whose socle is a finite\nsimple group of exceptional Lie type.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Nov 2015 02:01:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Sep 2018 22:13:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-05"}
