h a\nnumber of important lessons learned, suggest possible improvements, and\nrecommend this collective exploratory approach for future astronomical surveys\nor other extensive data sets with a sufficiently large user base. We also\nrelease open-source code of the web application and host an online demo version\nat http://des-exp-checker.pmelchior.net\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Nov 2015 05:13:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 May 2016 16:21:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-01"}
